title: #92Noon: Micheletti/Gleeman/Leo&Pohl/Lucia
description: Very Gopher Hockey heavy show, with Pat Micheletti in the first hour, a title reunion of Jordan Leopold & Johnny Pohl in studio, Don Lucia calls in to chat with PA, and in the middle of it all Aaron Gleeman hits on Howl and Twins.
